{"text": " Welcome to the practice, follow the air. Let us start by following the air. Follow the air coming in, going out of your body. Feel the air flow. Breathe naturally. Feel the air coming out of your body. Follow the air going in. Watch the air flow. Observe the air movement. Watch how the air is moving. Observe the air flow. Continue to watch the air movement. See if you can locate the air moving into your body. And now the air is moving inside you. Watch it coming out of your body. Keep observing the air going into you. And out of you. Watch the air. Stay here and observe the air. See how the air starts to move into you by itself without your effort. Watch how the air is coming out by itself. Stay here and watch the air. Watch the air. Allow your body to breathe naturally. Observe the air. Just stay here. Just watch the air movement or non-movement. Continue watching the air. Just settle here and watch the air. If it is moving or not moving. Don't participate. Just watch. See how the body breathes by itself. Watch how the air is moving by itself. How everything is happening by itself. Do not participate. Just watch. Witness this moment. Witness the presence of air. Just watch the air. Just keep watching the air. Slowly exhale, vertically down from the nose, from the chest, from the belly, pull the belly In, empty yourself of air and allow the air to come back into your body by itself Thank you", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 10.299999999999999, "end": 16.72, "text": " Welcome to the practice, follow the air.", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 264, 3124, 11, 1524, 264, 1988, 13, 51284], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.6194548240074744, "compression_ratio": 0.8888888888888888, "no_speech_prob": 0.09539148956537247, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 10.299999999999999, "end": 11.7, "probability": 0.9258824586868286}, {"word": " to", "start": 11.7, "end": 11.92, "probability": 0.9980039000511169}, {"word": " the", "start": 11.92, "end": 12.